001
002import java.util.ArrayList;
003import java.util.List;
004
005/**
006 * lyric
007 *
008 * @author matecsaba
009 */
010public class playerLyric {
011
012    private List<String> text = new ArrayList<String>();
013
014    /**
015     * modified
016     */
017    public long modified;
018
019    /**
020     * in range
021     *
022     * @param i number
023     * @return true if not, false if yes
024     */
025    public boolean inRange(int i) {
026        if (i < 0) {
027            return true;
028        }
029        if (i >= text.size()) {
030            return true;
031        }
032        return false;
033    }
034
035    /**
036     * title
037     *
038     * @return title
039     */
040    public String title() {
041        String s = text.get(0);
042        text.remove(0);
043        return s;
044    }
045
046    /**
047     * get line
048     *
049     * @param i line
050     * @return text
051     */
052    public String get(int i) {
053        return text.get(i);
054    }
055
056    /**
057     * delete line
058     *
059     * @param i line
060     */
061    public void del(int i) {
062        text.remove(i);
063    }
064
065    /**
066     * add line
067     *
068     * @param s text
069     */
070    public void add(String s) {
071        text.add(s);
072    }
073
074    /**
075     * add lines
076     *
077     * @param l text
078     */
079    public void addAll(playerLyric l) {
080        for (int i = 0; i < l.size(); i++) {
081            text.add(l.get(i));
082        }
083    }
084
085    /**
086     * find
087     *
088     * @param s text
089     * @return index
090     */
091    public int findFirst(String s) {
092        s = s.toLowerCase();
093        for (int i = 0; i < text.size(); i++) {
094            if (text.get(i).toLowerCase().equals(s)) {
095                return i;
096            }
097        }
098        return -1;
099    }
100
101    /**
102     * find
103     *
104     * @param s text
105     * @return index
106     */
107    public int findLast(String s) {
108        s = s.toLowerCase();
109        for (int i = text.size() - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
110            if (text.get(i).toLowerCase().equals(s)) {
111                return i;
112            }
113        }
114        return -1;
115    }
116
117    /**
118     * find
119     *
120     * @param s text
121     * @return index
122     */
123    public int findRegex(String s) {
124        for (int i = text.size() - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
125            if (text.get(i).matches(s)) {
126                return i;
127            }
128        }
129        return -1;
130    }
131
132    /**
133     * find
134     *
135     * @param s text
136     * @return count
137     */
138    public int findCount(String s) {
139        int o = 0;
140        s = s.toLowerCase();
141        for (int i = 0; i < text.size(); i++) {
142            if (text.get(i).toLowerCase().equals(s)) {
143                o++;
144            }
145        }
146        return o;
147    }
148
149    /**
150     * lines
151     *
152     * @return lines
153     */
154    public int size() {
155        return text.size();
156    }
157
158    /**
159     * break
160     *
161     * @param s text
162     * @return true if yes
163     */
164    public static boolean isBreak(String s) {
165        return s.equals("2br");
166    }
167
168    /**
169     * just words
170     *
171     * @param s string
172     * @return string
173     */
174    public static String justWords(String s) {
175        s = s.replaceAll("\\.", " ");
176        s = s.replaceAll("\\,", " ");
177        s = s.replaceAll("\\!", " ");
178        s = s.replaceAll("\\?", " ");
179        s = s.replaceAll("\\@", " ");
180        s = s.replaceAll("\\#", " ");
181        s = s.replaceAll("\\$", " ");
182        s = s.replaceAll("\\%", " ");
183        s = s.replaceAll("\\&", " ");
184        s = s.replaceAll("\\*", " ");
185        s = s.replaceAll("\\(", " ");
186        s = s.replaceAll("\\)", " ");
187        s = s.replaceAll("\\<", " ");
188        s = s.replaceAll("\\>", " ");
189        s = s.replaceAll("\\[", " ");
190        s = s.replaceAll("\\]", " ");
191        s = s.replaceAll("\\{", " ");
192        s = s.replaceAll("\\}", " ");
193        s = s.replaceAll("\\-", " ");
194        s = s.replaceAll("\\=", " ");
195        s = s.replaceAll("\\+", " ");
196        s = s.replaceAll("\\`", " ");
197        s = s.replaceAll("\\'", " ");
198        s = s.replaceAll("\\\"", " ");
199        s = s.replaceAll("\\;", " ");
200        s = s.replaceAll("\\:", " ");
201        s = s.replaceAll("\\\\", " ");
202        s = s.replaceAll("\\/", " ");
203        s = s.replaceAll("\\|", " ");
204        for (;;) {
205            String a = s;
206            s = s.replaceAll("\\ \\ ", " ");
207            if (a.equals(s)) {
208                break;
209            }
210        }
211        return s.trim();
212    }
213
214    /**
215     * is text
216     *
217     * @param s string
218     * @return true if yes
219     */
220    public static boolean isText(String s) {
221        return s.startsWith("1");
222    }
223
224    /**
225     * is tag
226     *
227     * @param s text
228     * @return true if yes
229     */
230    public static boolean isTag(String s) {
231        return s.startsWith("2");
232    }
233
234    /**
235     * just words
236     *
237     * @return string
238     */
239    public String justWords() {
240        String s = "";
241        if (text == null) {
242            return s;
243        }
244        for (int i = 0; i < text.size(); i++) {
245            s += " " + text.get(i).trim() + " ";
246        }
247        return s;
248    }
249
250    /**
251     * just content
252     *
253     * @return text
254     */
255    public playerLyric justContent() {
256        playerLyric res = new playerLyric();
257        for (int i = 0; i < text.size(); i++) {
258            String a = text.get(i).trim();
259            if (a.length() < 1) {
260                continue;
261            }
262            res.add(a);
263        }
264        return res;
265    }
266
267    /**
268     * line differs
269     *
270     * @param src source
271     * @return differing lines
272     */
273    public playerLyric linesDiffer(playerLyric src) {
274        playerLyric res1 = new playerLyric();
275        playerLyric res2 = new playerLyric();
276        for (int i = 0; i < src.size(); i++) {
277            String b = src.get(i);
278            String a = justWords(b);
279            if (a.length() < 1) {
280                continue;
281            }
282            res1.add(a);
283            res2.add(b);
284        }
285        for (int i = 0; i < text.size(); i++) {
286            int o = res1.findFirst(justWords(text.get(i)));
287            if (o < 0) {
288                continue;
289            }
290            res1.del(o);
291            res2.del(o);
292        }
293        return res2.justContent();
294    }
295
296    /**
297     * clear script lines
298     *
299     * @return cleared script
300     */
301    public playerLyric clearScript() {
302        playerLyric res = new playerLyric();
303        for (int i = 0; i < text.size(); i++) {
304            String a = text.get(i);
305            String b = a.trim().toLowerCase();
306            if (b.length() > 512) {
307                continue;
308            }
309            if (b.indexOf("document.createelement") >= 0) {
310                continue;
311            }
312            if (b.indexOf("document.getelement") >= 0) {
313                continue;
314            }
315            if (b.indexOf("<a href") >= 0) {
316                continue;
317            }
318            if (b.indexOf("can't find lyrics for") >= 0) {
319                continue;
320            }
321            if (b.indexOf("we don't have lyrics for") >= 0) {
322                continue;
323            }
324            if (b.indexOf("no lyrics found") >= 0) {
325                continue;
326            }
327            if (b.indexOf("<title>") >= 0) {
328                return new playerLyric();
329            }
330            res.add(a);
331        }
332        return res;
333    }
334
335}
